{"tid":1013280,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我修讀APL， 咁係咪令我入唔到某啲大學?","createTime":"2019-02-08T08:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T10:10:59.000Z","uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a52712b722fad25612f7da46ec8847d635b48503","tid":1013280,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:21:16.000Z","msg":"我已經讀緊， 但係又好似睇到有啲大學又唔當係一科<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !<br />\n<br />\n我係咪一定要四科主科加兩科選修， 而且達標大學要求同嗰科嘅要求! <br />\n<br />\n係咪咁先可以入到自己想入嘅大學同埋揀到想嘅科?<br />\n<br />\n 因為睇到有啲大學， 應用學習係冇計分方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> !"},{"pid":"9aed7eff60e0692df7707eeb84b0388b9d070177","tid":1013280,"uid":97267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"app唔洗讀 留啲時間溫書好鳩過啦<br />\n比你拎到優異成績都係當你dse拎3<br />\n唔溫書裸考dse都有3啦"},{"pid":"24efddbfd26be0d648637eb9d7d12591998b947e","tid":1013280,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:01:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6db3924acc35099e9f60ec869e6f0822958a619c","tid":1013280,"uid":219183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9aed7eff60e0692df7707eeb84b0388b9d070177","tid":1013280,"uid":97267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"app唔洗讀 留啲時間溫書好鳩過啦<br />\n比你拎到優異成績都係當你dse拎3<br />\n唔溫書裸考dse都有3啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"lv3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾多年赤柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n...達標水平<br />\n由2018年香港中學文憑考試開始*，學生的成績匯報細分為：「達標」、「達標並表現優異(I)」和「達標並表現優異(II)」。「達標並表現優異(I)」的表現水平等同香港中學文憑考試甲類科目第三級，而「達標並表現優異(II)」的表現水平等同第四級或以上。...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/cross-kla-studies/applied-learning/quality-assurance-and-articulation.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fcross-kla-studies%2Fapplied-learning%2Fquality-assurance-and-articulation.html&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1DsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=c287ade9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/cross-kla-studies/applied-learning/quality-assurance-and-articulation.html</a>"},{"pid":"d81e1d9c0c101efc76e77f18b451ac02c70a70bd","tid":1013280,"uid":5480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"如果我無記錯 UGC係唔當係APL一科 <br />\n最多你報嘅科係related 就有話有 優先考慮<br />\n利申讀過APL 個時有睇過下jupas 唔知依家仲係咪"},{"pid":"1358bd2cedeaf567494a0b2503e19a4215be12ec","tid":1013280,"uid":97267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6db3924acc35099e9f60ec869e6f0822958a619c","tid":1013280,"uid":219183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9aed7eff60e0692df7707eeb84b0388b9d070177","tid":1013280,"uid":97267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"app唔洗讀 留啲時間溫書好鳩過啦<br />\n比你拎到優異成績都係當你dse拎3<br />\n唔溫書裸考dse都有3啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"lv3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾多年赤柱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n...達標水平<br />\n由2018年香港中學文憑考試開始*，學生的成績匯報細分為：「達標」、「達標並表現優異(I)」和「達標並表現優異(II)」。「達標並表現優異(I)」的表現水平等同香港中學文憑考試甲類科目第三級，而「達標並表現優異(II)」的表現水平等同第四級或以上。...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/cross-kla-studies/applied-learning/quality-assurance-and-articulation.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fcross-kla-studies%2Fapplied-learning%2Fquality-assurance-and-articulation.html&d=SInmTBH44R2CRaFL2yHJ1DsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=c287ade9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/cross-kla-studies/applied-learning/quality-assurance-and-articulation.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"溫下書都有4啦<br />\n咪一鳩樣<br />\n溫書好過啦"}]}